>
  <div class="prose-page mx-auto max-w-3xl pt-10 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-(--tracking-tight)">
      Getting started
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-fg-muted">
      Phase 1 placeholder. The full guide lands in phase 4, covering
      FFI-overhead intuition (sourced from <code class="font-mono text-sm">docs/BASELINE.md</code>),
      how to read the Green / Yellow / Red / Archived verdicts, platform
      support across the six NAPI triples, and installation
      troubleshooting.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base text-fg-muted">
      For now, head to <a href="/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hot">the catalog</a>
      to install any package directly.
    </p>
